</center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ushaithin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Shaithin </A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br>  Posts: 320<br> <font color=#ffffff>(3/2/02 4:05 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Just a thought....</span><hr size=1> I've always liked the lower casting time idea for Harvest, the higher you go the less time needed to wait to recast it, I just wish it was a bit more to scale on the mana...It goes off a preset amount instead of ones INT and mana items which, If it did that I could live with the 10 minute wait because I would know I'm getting a bubble of mana in that time...not half or a quarter<br>
<br>
Another idea that was good was making it more a skill then spell..like Paladins Lay on hands...would save a slot, I'm the same way, I always have that spell memmed...first one to get added after I die but if it were a skill that would be a hell of a lot more handy because it would still be in the remaining time counter and not be reset like it does when I die and have to re-mem it.<br>
<br>
The PBAoE root is another good idea but the taunt is the one thing that worries me a bit...three MOB's and one AoE root to buy the Enchanter some time to mezz them all would be VERY handy but if something goes wrong your toast. I think the Enchanter should really have the spell more then us, yes yes, I know we have more PBAoE's then anyone out there but it would be more handy for them if you ask me....still there very good ideas <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ugalgamet.showPublicProfile?language=EN>galgamet</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br>  Posts: 28<br> <font color=#ffffff>(3/2/02 11:02 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Just a thought....</span><hr size=1> And you think PBAoE root would stick on those mobs?<br>
I'd expect at least 30% of the mobs to resist it.<br>
<br>
Flaeryen <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ushaithin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Shaithin </A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br>  Posts: 321<br> <font color=#ffffff>(3/2/02 11:14 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Just a thought....</span><hr size=1> They could up the resist check to make it more workable, its not like it going to hold them for 5 minutes...just enough to help the Enchanter to get a few mezzes off, The spell would would really be used like most Enchanters spells and thats to buy some time for the group. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ufraethir.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fraethir</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br>  Posts: 63<br> <font color=#ffffff>(3/4/02 12:10 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Just a thought....</span><hr size=1> If they implemented AoE root, expect it to be 4 target, and not PBAOE. That way, there's a chance you'll catch yourself in it (much like enchanters risk tagging themselves with their one and only AoE mes). It would also let you not be standing surrounded by mobs if/when they get rooted, which is a good thing. Once they're rooted, they're on prox-aggro, and I'd hate to be a wizard surrounded by four angry krups in Seb or something. It would hurt a LOT.<br>
<br>
